&lt;p id="p8wb3E"&gt;Rumored to arrive alongside the Galaxy S21 in January, Samsung’s followup to the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/21356260/samsung-galaxy-buds-live-review-wireless-earbuds-beans-design-specs-price"&gt;Galaxy Buds Live&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/2/24/21147654/samsung-galaxy-buds-plus-review-wireless-earbuds-sound-quality-battery-life"&gt;Galaxy Buds Plus&lt;/a&gt; has already leaked in three different colors: black, violet, and silver, again courtesy of &lt;a href="https://www.voice.com/profile/evan"&gt;Blass&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
